expression #Max_Heroes_In_Tourney 8
expression #fairgrounds_gold_winner 10
expression #Tourney_Entrance_Fee 10
expression #Percent_Chance_Goto_Combo_Tourney 60


//The distance at which a healer will be ressurected by their Home Guild
expression #Healer_Reborn_Distance 50

//Distance within which Heroes will find Fairgrounds attractive enough to consider participating in a Tourney
expression #Fairgrounds_Attraction_Range 1500

//Duration heroes stay in the fairgrounds for
expression #Compete_at_Fair_Duration 25000

//The delay that a Fairgrounds waits to open again after running a Tourney
expression #Fairgrounds_Open_Delay 60000

//Percent Chance that a Hero will look for Fairgrounds to Raise Stats
